{"id": "1425267168932794592", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "author_id": "289320818901778434", "author_name": "nikolazuli", "content": "while i wait for the diagram,\n1. ||Gramona freed a fragment of Keeper's consciousness from the gate and Gdoll trapped it in arc 2. (by coincidence. they're not working together)||\n2. ||Physically, the body Daff gave Keeper should be more or less identical, so there's essentially no difference. ||\n||However, Keeper's links to the awakeners are significantly weakened by the sheer distance and the fact they're not actually there, so it takes more effort to summon their \"images\" in battle. Combine that with the implication Keeper is taking more physical damage on average in arc2, the \"wet noodle keeper\" meme arises.||", "timestamp": "2025-10-07T23:42:53.257000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-07T23:43:37.520000+00:00"}
